call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Williams (LAC) is the last to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Beverley (LAC) places his forearm on Barrett's (NYK) hip as both players move around the pick. The contact steers Barrett away from his original path at the start of his drive.
Randle (NYK) makes contact to Harrell's (LAC) front during the upward shooting motion on his shot attempt.
Harkless (LAC) makes contact to Ntilikina's (NYK) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Randle (NYK) makes incidental contact to Williams' (LAC) arm after the release of the ball during his jump shot attempt.
Harrell (LAC) maintains a legal guarding position on Randle (NYK) during the drive.
On the pump fake Morris Sr. (NYK) draws Harkless LAC) towards him and Harkless initiates contact to Morris Sr.'s body during the upward shooting motion on his jump shot attempt.
Randle (NYK) maintains a legal guarding position during Williams' (LAC) driving shot attempt.
Morris Sr. (NYK) legally lifts his pivot and releases the ball to shoot.
Green (LAC) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Beverley (LAC) maintains a legal guarding position during Morris Sr.'s (NYK) jump shot attempt.
As Morris Sr. (NYK) pivots around Beverley (LAC), he makes marginal contact to Beverly's (LAC) side.
Barrett (NYK) commits a take foul on Williams (LAC).
